com.captiveimagination.jgn
Class JGN

java.lang.Object
  com.captiveimagination.jgn.JGN

public class JGN
extends java.lang.Object

This is the base class for JavaGameNetworking. Essentially, this is the static controller of this API. Any overrides or message registration is done here.

Author:
Matthew D. Hicks
